schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: This charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath cabin, nestled in a private, secluded neighborhood, offers a cozy retreat / vacation home with just over 800 square feet of living space with 4 car parking drive way to fit all vehicles to fit your needs. The classic log cabin exterior is surrounded by tall pine trees, and a front porch with a swing provides a tranquil space to enjoy the outdoors. Inside, you'll find an open living area with a classic stove, a well-equipped kitchen with a small bar style dining area, and two comfortable bedrooms. The clean and functional bathroom ensures your comfort. A chimney in the middle of the living room ensures warmth for those winter cold weathers coming up  providing a serene escape. Home has assumable loan, which will save you thousands out of pocket expenses, and home owners are open for sub to offers. Call for details.
